headline.main: Kennedy Center Goes for Ribald Laughs With District of Comedy Festival

keywords.value: Kennedy, John F, Center for the Performing Arts
keywords.name: organizations

snippet: From a James Carville roast to a Joan Rivers tribute, the four-day festival underlines the center’s resolve to expand its territory.
